## Group Currencies

Resources related to currencies in the API.

## Currency [/currency/{currency_name}]

A Currency object has the following attributes:

+ id
+ name
+ currency_code
+ stock_exchange
+ location
+ number_of_official_users

+ Parameters
    + currency_name: 1 (required, string) - Name of the Currency in form of a string

### View a Currency's Details [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            "currency": 
            {
                {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "US Dollars",
                    "currency_code": "USD",
                    "stock_exchange": "NYSE",
                    "location": "USA",
                    "number_of_official_users": 9
                }
            }            
        ]

